==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Delitescence
<hw>Del`i*tes"cence</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[See
<er>Delitescent</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Concealment; seclusion;
retirement.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The <qex>delitescence</qex> of mental activities.</q> <rj><qau>Sir
W. Hamilton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>The sudden disappearance of
inflammation.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Delitescency</ent>⟦br⟧
